# 🛒 E-Commerce REST API

## 🚀 Secure Spring Boot Backend for an E-Commerce Platform

This project provides REST APIs for **user authentication, product management, shopping cart operations, and order processing** using **Java, Spring Boot, Spring Security, and JWT**.

---

# 🧰 Tech Stack

* ☕ Java
* 🌱 Spring Boot
* 🔐 Spring Security + JWT
* 🗄 MySQL
* 📦 Maven
* 🧪 Postman
* 🐙 Git & GitHub

---

# ✨ Features

## 👤 User Module

* 📝 User Registration
* 🔑 JWT Login Authentication
* 👥 Role-Based Access (Admin / Customer)

## 📦 Product Module

* ➕ Add Products (Admin)
* ✏ Update Products
* ❌ Delete Products
* 🔍 Search Products
* 📋 View Product Catalog

## 🛒 Cart Module

* ➕ Add Items to Cart
* 🔄 Update Quantity
* ❌ Remove Items
* 👀 View Cart

## 📑 Order Module

* 🧾 Place Orders
* 📚 Order History
* 🚚 Track Order Status

